This paper focuses on optimizing the trajectory of UAVs for energy-efficient communication, which involves aspects of networking (communication throughput), robotics (UAV trajectory optimization), control systems (UAV propulsion energy consumption), information theory (energy efficiency definition), and artificial intelligence (design optimization). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
